Package edu.jhu.zpalmer2.spring2009.ai.hw6.shell.command

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EnvCommand
    This command displays the contents of the environment.
    HelpCommand  
    IterateCommand
    Iterates through one step of learning for the currently-loaded agent.
    LoadCommand
    Allows a persisted agent to be loaded.
    LoadWorldCommand
    Loads a world into memory from a specified file.
    MakeCommand
    This command allows the creation of reinforcement learning agents from within the shell.
    MetricsCommand
    This command displays human-readable metrics data to the user.
    QuitCommand  
    SaveCommand
    This command can be used to persist an agent to disk.
    SetCommand
    This command allows the changing of variables in the shell's environment.
    SimulateCommand
    Runs a simulation using the policy of the current agent.
    VarHelpCommand
    This command provides help information regarding variables in the environment.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    CommandFailureException
    This class of exception is thrown when a command cannot be executed successfully.
